{"body": "I'm sorry. There is a reason to not accept this kind of changes, if we start to accept things like: \"Changing the hash syntax to 1.9\", \"Replace unless with if\", \"Change the indentation of code\" we will start to receive a lot of pull request doing these changes.\nThis will lead a lot of effort of the core team to review and merge these pull request, without any real gain to the framework.\n\nI really appreciate your effort to make this pull request and I really want to see more contributions from you.\n\nThank you for the guides notes.\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6276435", "created_at": "2012-06-12T17:11:31Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6714#issuecomment-6276435", "updated_at": "2012-06-12T17:11:31Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6714, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523804f7bd3543c15100c688"}, "id": 6276435, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/r